OL,3,CPrime Minister apologises to the
OL,4,Cfamilies of Springhill victims
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister has apologised to
OL,7,Fthe families of five people shot dead
OL,8,Fin west Belfast in 1972.
OL,10,FThree teenagers, a parish priest and a
OL,11,Ffather-of-six were killed in the
OL,12,FSpringhill/Westrock area on the night
OL,13,Fof July 9.
OL,15,FThose who died were Father Noel
OL,16,FFitzpatrick, 42, Patrick Butler, 38,
OL,17,FJohn Dougal, 16, David McCafferty, 15,
OL,18,Fand Margaret Gargan, 13.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
