OL,3,CPrime Minister apologises to the
OL,4,Cfamilies of Springhill victims
OL,6,FAn inquest into their deaths found
OL,7,Fthat two Army soldiers "overreacted
OL,8,Fand lost control". In April, a coroner
OL,9,Fruled that the force used was not
OL,10,Freasonable.
OL,12,FSpeaking during Prime Minister's
OL,13,Fquestions on Wednesday, Sir Keir
OL,14,FStarmer said: "The findings of the
OL,15,Frecent Springhill inquest into the
OL,16,Ftragic deaths in July 1972 of Father
OL,17,FNoel Fitzpatrick, Patrick Butler,
OL,18,FMargaret Gargan, David McCafferty and
OL,19,FJohn Dougal are sobering.
OL,26,@oD@XOUpD@QO]vD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
