PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1780665075
OL,3,CPrime Minister apologises to the
OL,4,Cfamilies of Springhill victims
OL,6,FThe families of those killed had
OL,7,Fcalled for a public apology and had
OL,8,Frecently criticised the government
OL,9,Fover its "silence" after the inquest
OL,10,Ffindings.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister has also written to
OL,13,Fthe families individually to
OL,14,Fpersonally apologise for what happened
OL,15,Fand the grief and suffering they have
OL,16,Fendured.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
